{
  "id": 5104141688635392,
  "name": "CSS `text-fit` property",
  "summary": "Scales the font size of text nodes to perfectly fit the width of its containing box.\n\nThis property allows developers to ensure headlines or dynamic content fill the available horizontal space without manual font-size calculations or complex JavaScript workarounds. It provides a robust, CSS-native solution for responsive typography that maintains visual alignment across different screen sizes and varying text lengths.\n",
